# Capacitor native platforms (generated — rebuild with `npm run cap:sync`)
ios
# `infra/ios/` stages iOS compliance artifacts (Privacy Manifest, Fastlane
# configs) that are copied into `ios/App/App/` during bring-up — keep them
# tracked even though the generated project isn't.
!infra/ios/
!infra/ios/**
# android is tracked so we can customise AndroidManifest, Gradle, icons, etc.
